[h3]Reaping & Total Wars[/h3]
[list]
[*]Winning a Reaping war on surrender now transfers every eligible pop instead of being capped by the current escalation tier.
[*]Auto-raiding occupied planets in a Reaping war ignores the tier cap — how many pops you take each month is driven by stationed armies alone.
[*]Total wars (End Threat, etc.) no longer prompt for opportunistic raiding. Raiding is already allowed in those wars.
[/list]

[h3]Machine Despoilers[/h3]
[list]
[*]Reworked starting-pop setup to handle vanilla's species identity swap on certain origins. The battery species is now identified by trait rather than by founder-species identity.
[/list]

[h3]Bug Fixes[/h3]
[list]
[*]Opportunistic raiding's Influence cost now shows correctly in the authorization tooltip.
[*]Fixed missing modifier localisation for livestock and processing trade value.
[*]Fixed a missing tradition tooltip for Boarding Cables.
[/list]
